      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPANISH ARMADA (1) turned in a plain run last time when sixth at Shepparton over 390m behind Piebald (23.03) in a Grade 5. The form from his last run stacks up well. Better than last start and worth following up. BERSERKER VIKING (3) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from six starts. Was out of the placings last time (25.76) at Shepparton in a Grade 5, finishing fourth and beaten 5.5 lengths. Can hit the frame with the right run. DANCE LADY DANCE (2) settled down midfield and held her position to the line when finishing 4th (25.99) at Ballarat. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Expected to feature in the finish. BROOMBRAE FRITZ (4) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish.",
